  "remarks": "JSC “North Western Regional Center of Almaz Antey Concern Obukhovsky Plant” is one of the largest enterprises in the Russian defence industry and, besides civil production, creates weapons systems and military equipment. It provides communications, air defence systems and missiles that the Russian Armed Forces are using in the war of aggression against Ukraine.",
